            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "j9Pk2o",
              "name": "nb",
              "fill": "$c:--muted-foreground",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "• Toggle defaults to Search when caps.mods.registry is set; otherwise only From URL is shown.\n• Search → GET /servers/{name}/mods/registry/search?q= (debounced, ≥2 chars). Expanding a card → GET …/projects/{id}/versions. The API filters by the active loader + gameVersion.\n• Install reuses POST /servers/{name}/mods/install with the chosen file's downloadUrl — no new install path, same SSRF allowlist.\n• A 501 (no registry for this game, e.g. Terraria) hides Search and falls back to From URL.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$c:--font-secondary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
