            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Z3UC1",
              "name": "nb",
              "fill": "$c:--muted-foreground",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "• Browser: opens to a popular list (empty query); Sort = Downloads/Updated/Relevance; chips filter by category; Load more pages via offset. Same GET …/mods/registry/search?type=mod&sort=&offset= for both browsers (type=modpack for the Modpacks tab).\n• Modpacks tab shows only when the template declares capabilities.mods.registry.modpacks. Install differs by game: Minecraft pins the pack via POST /servers/{name}/modpack (sets TYPE=MODRINTH + MODRINTH_MODPACK, restarts — one active pack, shown as a banner); Valheim resolves the pack's dependencies (GET …/projects/{id}/modpack) and installs each via /mods/install (extracted into bepinex/plugins).\n• A 501 (no registry) hides Browse; no modpacks block hides the Modpacks tab.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$c:--font-secondary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        }
