              "content": "• Clone server requires the operator role — same gate as other non-destructive lifecycle actions.\n• Transfer ownership, Wipe world data, and Delete server require the server's owner OR the operator role; collaborators and viewers never see these three.\n• Both entry points (Servers list row ⋯, and the Server Detail header More actions button) render the same menu; items are hidden rather than disabled when the caller lacks the role.\n• Wipe world data and Delete server are destructive — labeled in $c:--destructive, matching the existing danger-dialog convention.",
