              "fill": "$c:--muted-foreground",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "• Reuses the same Kubernetes event → message mapping already used by the Overview Recent events card (reason → human text, source = reportingComponent).\n• Filtering (All / Info / Warnings) happens client-side against the already-fetched event list — no new query params.\n• Polls faster than the Overview card while the server's phase isn't Running (e.g. every 3s during Provisioning/Terminating), falling back to the normal interval once Running.\n• Inserted into the tab strip right after Overview; always shown — Kubernetes events exist regardless of the game template's declared capabilities.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$c:--font-secondary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        }
