              "content": "• Saving materializes/updates a BackupSchedule named <server>-auto, owned by the GameServer; deleting the policy (or the server) deletes it.\n• Overlaps the standalone Backups-tab schedule UI — the Backups tab badges this schedule \"Managed by server settings\" and warns if a server ends up with more than one schedule.\n• Suspend maps to BackupSchedule.spec.suspend; the cron field validates against robfig/cron/v3 syntax client-side before submit.",
