              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "• Empty retention buckets are omitted from the payload; the operator/restic treat 0 or absent as \"keep everything\" for that bucket.\n• The \"Managed by server settings\" badge marks the <server>-auto BackupSchedule owned by the Settings → Scheduled backups panel — it's read-only from the Backups tab.\n• The warning line appears whenever a server has more than one BackupSchedule pointing at it, regardless of which one is auto-managed.",
