              "name": "nb",
              "fill": "$c:--muted-foreground",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "• Shown only when the module's catalog entry has a source with type==\"upload\" (added via Modules → Sources & Upload, not a registered ModuleSource).\n• Calls DELETE /modules/sources/{source}/upload/{module}; distinct from Uninstall, which deletes the live Module CR but leaves the bundle in place.\n• On success, invalidates the modules catalog query — the card either disappears (if not installed) or drops the \"Remove upload\" action (if a non-upload source now serves the same module).",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "$c:--font-secondary",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
